The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Thursday, November 4, 2004

 Road to avoid

 SP Mukherjee Road, near Kalighat Metro station. Dug up for laying water pipeline.

 Fashion

 Minawala?s ?Bollywood By Design?, an exhibition of couture jewellery and watches, at Taj Bengal, from 11 am.

 An exclusive collection of Benarasi saris on view at Weavers Studio, 10 am to 6 pm.

