 Romeo at Jeannette will be staged by Kalyani Kalamandalam at Bharatiyam, Salt Lake, 6.30 pm.

 Fair

 Consumer 2004, featuring pavilions on automobiles, banking, insurance, IT, FMCG, real estate and others, organised by Confederation of Indian Industry, will be opened on the Maidan, 3 pm.

